$(1)$ Find the maximum distance from point $P$ to the curve $C_{2}$;

$(2)$ If the curve $C_{3}$: $\theta= \frac {\pi}{4}$ intersects curve $C_{1}$ at points $A$ and $B$, find the area of $\triangle ABC_{1}$.
